    <section class="section privacy-policy">
      <div class="container">
        <div data-w-id="ee4c9493-272b-6921-5816-7d90c914124b" class="privacy-policy-content">
          <div class="privacy-policy-rich-content">
            <div class="privacy-policy-rich-text w-richtext">
              <h2>Our commitment to your privacy</h2>
              <p>National AI Technologies (NAIT) operates Oman’s sovereign AI platform, serving government institutions, private enterprises, and academic organizations. Protecting the information entrusted to us is central to our mandate. This policy explains what information we collect through our website and services, how we use it, and the choices available to you.</p>
              <h2>Information we collect</h2>
              <p>When you contact us or request a demonstration, we collect the details you provide, such as your name, work email address, organization, and the content of your message. When you browse our website, we collect standard technical information, including your IP address, browser type, pages visited, and the time and duration of your visit. We collect only what is needed to respond to your request and to operate, secure, and improve our services.</p>
              <h2>How we use your information</h2>
              <p>We use the information we collect to respond to enquiries, evaluate partnership and integration requests, deliver and improve our services, maintain the security of our platform, and meet our legal and regulatory obligations in the Sultanate of Oman. We do not sell personal information, and we do not use it for purposes unrelated to our mandate.</p>
              <h2>Data sovereignty</h2>
              <p>Data sovereignty is the foundation of our platform. Information processed through NAIT services is hosted on secure national infrastructure within the borders of the Sultanate of Oman. Our systems are built, managed, and operated by Omani talent, under clear governance and in alignment with Oman Vision 2040.</p>
              <h2>Security</h2>
              <p>We protect information through layered security controls, including encryption in transit and at rest, governed access on a need-to-know basis, continuous monitoring, and strict operational procedures across the full data lifecycle. Our security practices are designed to meet enterprise and government requirements on par with international benchmarks.</p>
              <h2>Cookies</h2>
              <p>Our website uses a small number of cookies and similar technologies to remember your language preference and to understand how the website is used so we can improve it. You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect some features, such as language selection.</p>
              <h2>Sharing of information</h2>
              <p>We share information only when it is necessary to deliver our services, when required by the laws of the Sultanate of Oman, or when you ask us to. Service providers who support our operations are bound by confidentiality obligations and may not use your information for any other purpose.</p>
              <h2>Data retention</h2>
              <p>We keep personal information only for as long as it is needed for the purposes described in this policy or as required by applicable law. When information is no longer needed, we delete it securely.</p>
              <h2>Your rights</h2>
              <p>You may request access to the personal information we hold about you, ask us to correct or delete it, or object to how it is used. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at contact@nait.om. We will respond within a reasonable period.</p>
              <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
              <p>We may update this policy from time to time to reflect changes in our services or legal obligations. The latest version will always be published on this page with the date of the last update. Significant changes will be communicated clearly on our website.</p>
              <h2>Contact us</h2>
              <p>If you have any questions about this policy or how we handle your information, contact our team at contact@nait.om. We typically respond within two business days.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section-line left"></div>
        <div class="section-line right"></div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="blank-div-wrapper border-none">
